  <brief_title>Open Label, Dose Escalation Phase I Study of AZD2281</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I, Open-label, Dose Escalation Study to Assess the Safety and Tolerability of AZD2281 Following Single and Multiple Oral Doses in Patients in Japan With Advanced Solid Malignancies</official_title>
  <sponsors>
